{
  "stem": "2133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The rest of her family-- she had two sisters living in New York, and a brother was living in Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She just-- she just always liked-- she liked Europe.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- I suppose it was a little bit difficult-- at that time, in those years, it was a little bit difficult, even in America.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I am sure that [CLEARS THROAT] it would have been far better if she would have remained here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were aware of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard-- because my mother had a very close friend of her who was living in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, matter of fact, she had sent-- when the anti-Semitism start-- started in Germany and they start to persecute the Jews, her son came to visit us and stayed with us for quite a while, you know.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't-- I don't even believe that he went back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He emigrated someplace else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was terrible.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember it real well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what year it was when it came to power-- Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'33?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I heard that on the radio, or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I-- I was a young fellow at the time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I heard him say, you know, that I'm going to try to kill every Jews I possibly can.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the one who will survive, I make it sure that they're going to lose some member of their family, that they never be happy in life.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- it-- in '33, so I must have been-- I was born in-- about 9 years old, 10 years old.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We spoke either a little bit of Czech and-- and Hungarian, because it was-- you know, my late years in school was in a Hungarian school.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
